          "range": false
        }
      ],
      "title": "SSD Life Remaining (vendor wear attr)",
      "description": "Normalized SSD wear (100 = new). Sourced from whichever vendor attribute a disk exposes (wear_leveling_count, media_wearout_indicator, ssd_life_left, percent_lifetime_remain). SSDs that expose none, plus all HDDs, do not appear; NVMe endurance is shown in the NVMe row.",
